{"id":282036,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-维权人士废墟上拉出横幅，抗议无锡警方/","date":"2013-03-04T08:00:46Z","modified":"2013-03-04T08:00:46Z","title":"维权网 | 维权人士废墟上拉出横幅，抗议无锡警方拘留丁红芬（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，倪文华与南通维权人士钱琴夫妇、冯兰美夫妇、单丽华等一起，在如皋的一堆废墟（原是冯兰美的家，因政府非法强拆成废墟）上拉出“丁红芬营救黑监狱受害人有功”的横幅，抗议无锡警方拘留丁红芬。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨，有无锡警察乘两辆特勤车（车号：苏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">FB1377</span><span>、苏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">FB710Q9</span><span>）到丁红芬住处，将她抓走，并作出给予</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天拘留的决定。其理由竟然是，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>丁红芬在北京最高检门前扰乱公共场所秩序。法律工作者指出，《治安处罚法》第九十九条规定：“公安机关办理治安案件的期限，自受理之日起不得超过三十日；案情重大、复杂的，经上一级公安机关批准，可以延长三十日。”也就是说，对治安处罚从立案起，最长不得超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>天，而无锡警方对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>个月以前发生的事，才作出处罚显然属于程序违法。其真实原因是，丁红芬勇敢地营救吴国新出黑监狱，无锡警方对丁红芬进行报复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>与丁红芬一起参与营救行动的沈爱斌也遭受当局的迫害，随即被关进官方所称的法制教育学习班，即黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4Gjg1hliMo4/UTQ8mao8RVI/AAAAAAAAeVo/GjZEJtqD_hY/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130304140902.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"493\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4Gjg1hliMo4/UTQ8mao8RVI/AAAAAAAAeVo/GjZEJtqD_hY/s640/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130304140902.png\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--v6XBkC3uZM/UTQ8oupi7XI/AAAAAAAAeVw/nrrG21r_weQ/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130304140924.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"473\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--v6XBkC3uZM/UTQ8oupi7XI/AAAAAAAAeVw/nrrG21r_weQ/s640/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130304140924.png\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[171,16910]}